node.text:
Doing a little back workout on Day 2 in Puerto Vallarta at Vidanta Resort. Grand Luxxe hotel gym. 
@Regenamexclinicpv will be doing the stem cell treatment. My first treatment went extremely well and I would say eliminated 30-40% of the pain. I’m hoping to get another 30-40% elimination on this treatment. Everything about the process is great here. The Vidanta Resort is the best resort hotel ever. The rooms have full kitchens, the staff is the best ever. They have everything you want and need here. I am so lucky to have found this location. #vidantaresorts #regenamexclinicpv

node.title: Day 2, Puerto Vallarta for Stem Cell

node.text: New to the Ronnie Coleman Signature Series Classic, it The Kings Royalty Package. Anyone who purchases it will receive a Private one on one with the King in the Silver Spur Room. All day reserved seat in the Kings Royal Court. Custom One Time only limited edition cap signed by the King. Personal autographed picture by the King. Photos by the photographer of their special time with Ronnie to be emailed after the event. This Meet the King Royalty Package is limited to the first 20 people who purchase it. You can purchase at Ronniecolemanclassic.com.

node.text:
I had a blast in Orlando last week shooting some content for the upcoming release of my new YEAH BUDDY™️ App. 
We had some down time so I decided to take @seanathletics & @williamrcss bowling. You know your boy had to show them how it’s suppose to be done…nothing to it but to do it!!!
Yeah Buddy, the slap on the back got me hype 👑
#YeahBuddy #RCSS #RonnieColeman #Bowling #TeamRCSS

node.text: My autobiography “Yeah Buddy” is now available in Japanese. You can order the Japanese version from Amazon Japan. In your web browser type Amazon.co.jp. You can order it from any where in the world. We don’t have it on the American site yet but we do have the Spanish and English version available on amazon.com.#yeahbuddy

node.text: Had a great time this weekend being inducted into the Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame. This is by far my greatest honor of all time because this is my home state inducting me and it’s for all sports and genres.  You have to be nominated by someone on the selection committee. There are 150 people nominated every year. Then from those 150 names 11 are chosen to be inducted. I was inducted on my first ballot on the nomination. I am also the first bodybuilder to be ever inducted into this Hall of Fame.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ronnie Coleman on June 24, 2021. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: Being inducted into the Louisiana Sports’s Hall of Fame this weekend. This is probably the biggest Honor I’ve ever received. Thanks and a very much appreciated to all those who are congratulating me on this honor. You guys really have no idea how much this means to me.

node.text: Had a wonderful trip to MEXICO but now it’s time to go home. Thanks to our hosts Daniel and Melanie Carruthers. This was my second trip to get stem cells from @regenamexclinicpv. My first trip was a huge success back in February with a great reduction in pain. I’m quite sure this trip will be just as successful when the procedure finally kicks in gear.

node.text: Yes sir I am here in Puerto Vallarta at the Vidanta Resort staying at the Grand Luxxe Hotel and training on-site at the Grand Luxxe Hotel Tower 2 gym. This gym is very special just like the rooms at the resort. This gym is very comparable to any professional gym like Gold’s gym or World’s gym. I can’t put Metroflex gym in there because Metroflex has no A/C. Still getting it in despite being on a mini vacation with the wife and kids and being here for my next stem cell treatment. #vidantaresorts  @regenamexclinicpv #regenamexclinicpv
